modName: Ashara Princess of the Woods - UNPB BBP
summary: A conversion of the Princess of the Woods set by SydneyB for UNPB-BBP with working weight slider. It requires SydneyB\'s original mod.
descriptionHtml:
A conversion of the Princess of the Woods set by SydneyB for UNPB-BBP with working weight slider. It requires SydneyB\'s original mod.

English is not my native language so sorry for my mistakes.

Update 0.2: Fur collar converted
Update 0.3: fix by SydneyB so the armor won\'t turn invisible underwater. Thanks alot!

Required mods (don\'t forget to endorse them):
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18008]Ashara Princess of the Woods for UNP[/url]
(Optional) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/23626]DreamBurrows Princess of The Woods Retexture[/url] Retexture used in the screenshots
The UNPB body replacer with BBP support: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/37900/]UNPB REDUX PROJECT[/url] OR [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/20227/?]Troublemakers Clothing[/url]

Does not work without BBP.

Installation:
First install the required mods
Use NMM as usual and overwrite when asked
Manual installation: open archive, extract meshes folder into data folder and overwrite when asked.

Credits and thanks:
SydneyB for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18008]Ashara Princess of the Woods for UNP[/url]
DreamBurrows for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/23626]DreamBurrows Princess of The Woods Retexture[/url]
calyps and xp32 for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14899]UNP BLESSED BODY UNPB - With Optional BBP Breast Physics[/url]
dimon99 for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709]DIMONIZED UNP female body[/url]
author: belisariu
